<P>> The progess of level should be Linear.

<BR>&gt; PVP will become vilable when a greater range of levels is a
<BR>&gt; challange. As it stands now, with a 4 level span, your not going
<BR>&gt; to run into enough people to engage with.
<P>WRONG!....in any zone i ever spent a significant amout of time in 90% of the people in that zone were +/-4 to me.....at any given level there is an optimal zone (others are either too weak or too difficult to be efficeient) and players of similar leel will gather there naturaly
<P>That is just one of
<BR>&gt; the many problems that PVP and the
<P>niggardly
<BR>nice use of headline buzzword......did you know what that word meant two weeks ago?
<P>level system
<BR>&gt; produces. The level must be expanded atlease to 10 levels.
<BR>&gt; This will not happen, not in time however.
<P>&gt; The blind eye that EQ has cast toward the PK part of the game is
<BR>&gt; a trajedy
<P>&gt; Leshy
